headline: 4 Diversified Operations Stocks to Watch Despite Industry Headwinds
summary: The prospects of the Zacks Diversified Operations industry are hindered by weaknesses in the manufacturing sector and ongoing supply chain challenges. HON, MMM, CIB and ITT are notable stocks in the industry.
